ajor part of the policy. There is stress on management of water resources in a manner which provides access to drinking water and provides employment opportunities. Periodical assessment of ground water potential, watershed management and research on hydrometeorology is part of the policy which is closely related to climate change mitigation and adaptation. Coastal land management and development is part of the policy. Positive.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "779ea6e2-bf44-4836-8fb4-c44d149554b1": {"__data__": {"id_": "779ea6e2-bf44-4836-8fb4-c44d149554b1", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/aphdr-technical-background-paper-2012/06", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "APHDR Technical Background Paper 2012/06", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/aphdr-technical-background-paper-2012/06", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "e3ecf72c7902f42dbc71395496b5f8682328679b14525e2587518ed84cc69474"}, "2": {"node_id": "12fa74a1-e42d-415f-94eb-3cd1a7ef453d", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/aphdr-technical-background-paper-2012/06", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "471324746cd806eeb192c68ad75ab32d67470e4d515de2b297ad2a7ed037799e"}}, "hash": "49dcb1be2eb9686478fa15d34ea10206a215c9b4f7fa4ea13116eefbc23a2e1b", "text": "Coastal land management and development is part of the policy. P